            "list": [
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/be10b57bd4fce45a364e71e0475c4e27_4012052741101610815.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>These drums were created by the Order of Skeptics' ancestors. Hit them according to a specific method to cause the elemental power within to resound...</p><p>There are three ways of hitting these drums. <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Normal Attacks</span> will create a light sound, while <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Plunging Attacks</span> will create a heavy one. <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Stay still</span> to create a pause.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/be10b57bd4fce45a364e71e0475c4e27_5405439180465797537.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>There are often drum scores near Kory Drums. The scores are comprised of various leaves that are split into three categories: <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">empty, half, and full</span>, which correspond to <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">pause, light, and heavy</span> beats.</p><p>Read the scores from left to right and top to bottom.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/23/77454259/be10b57bd4fce45a364e71e0475c4e27_3697499409837282174.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>After your performance begins, each glimmer of a Kory Drum represents one beat. Follow the score and the beat to create the corresponding drumbeat and complete your performance!</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/3"
              }
            ],
